entries.femaleVariant: Listen! Hear me! The final battle has come, the war to wipe us off the face of the earth!
The bomb? The bomb of twenty-three was just the beginning! A hiccup! A humble messenger!
Death! Death will bury us all! The corporate thrones will collapse, the flames of Pacifica will reach the stars!
Meat and steel, blood and chrome! Together they'll flow! The old powers fall, fall, fall into the grave of the world!
Arasaka, Militech, Biotechnica, Petrochem â€“ all scratch-wiped from memory!
But wait! Let this be our comfort in our time of tears! There are metals precious and common, but skulls and bones? They're the same!
The puppets and puppet-masters! The same, to dust! Have faith, for Santa Muerte comes for us all!
It is here! The final Judgement! Believe! The great leveler, the era of blind nothing!
